data.title: Bike Carrier Roof - Thule FreeRide 532
data.description:
How to install the Thule FreeRide 532 bike rack on the roof of your car? This video will show you step by step how to do it. 

Thule FreeRide 532
The functional and easy to use bike carrier fulfilling all basic needs.

- Frame holder with quick-lock, fits most frame sizes up to 80 mm.
- Quick-release straps with wheel protection hold the wheels securely in place (adjustable for different wheel sizes).
- Lockable - bike to bike carrier, bike carrier to load carrier (locks included).
- The maximum allowed weight per bike is 17 kg.
- T-track adapters (20x20mm) are included for mounting on Thule WingBar Edge, Thule WingBar, Thule SlideBar, and Thule AeroBar.
- Fulfils the City Crash norm.

Learn more at www.thule.com

data.title: Bike Carrier Rear - Thule Clip On High
data.description:
Watch this step by step instruction video and learn how easy it is to install the Thule ClipOn High rear bike rack by yourself. 

Thule ClipOn High 9105, 9106
The fast mounting and foldable bike carrier designed for station wagons and hatchbacks (for 2 bikes).

- The raised position of the carrier keeps the rear lights and number plate visible.
- All parts in contact with the car and bikes are coated with rubber for extra protection.
- All bike frame holders are detachable for convenient mounting of bikes.
- Easy to mount to the rear door with a unique snap-on system.
- Quick-release straps, adjustable for different wheel sizes.
- Extendable wheel trays for large bikes.
- Quickly folds for easy storage.
- Outer bike position lockable to carrier.
- This product does not have universal fit. The ClipOn High carrier comes in two versions (9105 and 9106) having different tube diameters fitting different car models. Please visit Thule.com for information related to specific car models.

Learn more at www.thule.com

data.title: Bike Carrier Roof - Thule ProRide 591
data.description:
Watch this video and learn step by step how to install the Thule ProRide 591 bike rack on the roof of your car. 

Thule ProRide 591
The best and most convenient roof mounted bike carrier on the market -- for bikes up to 20 kg.

- The uniquely designed frame holder and the wheel tray automatically position the bike to the correct place allowing it to rest securely against the frame holder while securing it.
- The convenient height of the turning knob makes the final tightening quick and easy.
- The only roof mounted bike carrier on the market with a capacity to carry bikes up to 20 kg.
- Fits bike frames up to 100mm (oval 80x100mm, round 22-80mm)
- Quick-release straps with wheel protection hold the wheels securely in place (adjustable for different wheel sizes).
- Can easily be fitted on either side of the car roof.
- This carrier is pre-assembled, no tools are required.
- Lockable - bike to bike carrier, bike carrier to load carrier (locks included).
- T-track adapters (20x20mm) are included for mounting on Thule WingBar Edge, Thule WingBar, Thule SlideBar, and Thule AeroBar.
- Fulfils the City Crash norm.

Learn more at www.thule.com

data.title: Bike Carrier Rear - Thule ClipOn
data.description:
How to install the Thule ClipOn bike rack on the rear of your car? This video will show you step by step how to do it. 

Thule ClipOn 9103, 9104
The snap-on bike carrier with smart features, perfect for station wagons and hatchbacks (for 3 bikes).

- All parts in contact with the car and bikes are coated with rubber for extra protection.
- Easy to mount to the rear door with a unique snap-on system.
- Quickly folds for easy storage.
- Possible to attach Thule Light board 976.
- Use Thule Bike Frame Adapter 981 for fitting of bikes with non-standard frames (e.g. ladies' bikes, BMXs, downhill bikes).
- This product does not have universal fit. The ClipOn carrier comes in two versions (9103 and 9104) having different tube diameters fitting different car models. Please visit Thule.com for information related to specific car models.

Learn more at www.thule.com

data.title: Bike Carrier Towbar - Thule HangOn
data.description:
Are you looking for a way to transport your bike? Watch this video and find out how to install Thule HangOn bike rack on the towbar of your car

Thule HangOn 9708
The basic, tiltable and easy to use bike carrier (for 4 bikes).

- Strong coupling that needs no pre-adjustment for fixing.
- Soft, protective frame holders keep the bikes in place.
- Tiltable for access to the trunk.
- Carrier lockable on tow bar with accessory Thule Lock 957.
- Use Thule Bike Frame Adapter 981 for fitting of bikes with non-standard frames (e.g. ladies' bikes, BMXs, downhill bikes).
- Folds flat for easy storage and handling.

Learn more at www.thule.com
